com.qualcomm.hardware.modernrobotics

Class ModernRoboticsI2cGyro

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • com.qualcomm.hardware.modernrobotics.ModernRoboticsI2cGyro

  • public class ModernRoboticsI2cGyro
extends <any>
    ModernRoboticsI2cGyro supports the Modern Robotics integrating gyro.

    This sensor contains an L3GD20 MEMS three-axis digital output gyroscope. Internally, the chip is labelled (e.g.) "AGD2 2437 JR4IJ".

    See Also:
    MR Integrating Gyro, MR sensor documentation, L3GD20
